        </li>
        <li>
            <a href="#" class="text-teal-600 hover:underline">Book Nook</a>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Reviews of my latest reads.</p>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <hr class="my-6 border-gray-300">
    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-teal-700 mb-4">About the Author</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
        Hi, I’m [Your Name]! I love sharing stories about travel, tech, and life’s little moments. Follow me on social media for more!
    </p>
</aside>
